{
  "texts": [
    "Introducing a learnable HU-intensity filter is a key innovation of our work.",
    "We examined the performance of the learning parameter with both random initialization and constant initialization.",
    "We observed that the model provides improved results when we make the interval learnable instead of using a non-learner model.",
    "The input at various intensity ranges is created by making a custom function.",
    "In this function, we specify the number of branches that are needed."
  ]
}